Woertz – Your partner for comprehensive solutions
Woertz is the leading provider of comprehensive installation systems and components for electrical installation technology in buildings and infrastructure. These networks form the unseen lifelines of the technical configuration of buildings.
A wide variety of technologies are firmly anchored at Woertz. This fact allows us to address different customer requirements with a wide range of systems and services that meet these demands. Product solutions from Woertz are economical, reliable and have a long service life.
